title: Ranked Gods (God Tier Team)
body:
Looking to make an unbeatable team comp to boost us all to challenger. Need people who are pretty chill about losing and don't get tilted easily and can spam games. Long-term team. Needs to be able to play these champs well (mechanically ;) ) in their roles  :

Aiming for a 9001% winrate or above. 
{{sticker:zombie-brand-mindblown}} 

Top - Me :P
Mid - Anivia, Brand, Azir, Lissandra, Katarina, Nautilus, Yasuo, Fizz
Jungle - Amumu, Malphite, Maokai, Zac, Volibear, Nautilus
A(D/P)C - Jinx, Twitch, Sivir, Draven, Miss Fortune
Support - Taric, Soraka, Zyra, Braum
